案組跟進。"},{"pid":"fd072548de58b0a1bfbe1b73d93c21fcceb67a80","tid":1714261,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e323fb5a62a0fbe9326be4fb2a34cabe8b103a83","tid":1714261,"uid":33222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f2ff6538cfa8d36ae0467c9b4ae003cd52d90c","tid":1714261,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d010c2c4dc620fb5489fdb2221027f44fedc3e6f","tid":1714261,"uid":33222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:34:44.000Z","msg":"唔係話中大教授們去保釋咩？保釋咗都要上court？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:43:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:45:43.000Z","msg":"下 我係琴晚睇立場 沈祖堯話拉咗五個 有3個係中大學生 保釋咗3人 另外2人睇醫生<br />\n唔通佢呃人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:48:34.000Z","msg":"唔好咁易比人帶住走"},{"pid":"3a422f5953e7f0f2b96a0cda010c29e5fcdcd574","tid":1714261,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:48:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db773f018d561afb843b6304b0b3ea375852216f","tid":1714261,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:50:55.000Z","msg":"11.11中大義士被控暴動 將於 9:30A.M. 沙田裁判法院提堂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713475</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7a248c46691b0d1803f9a704495ac4aa67b25191","tid":1714261,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}